3032,"uid":109453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb89aaf91fc6006fcf0a7352c6dce5f05f84b7ff","tid":2203032,"uid":106783,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T06:52:56.000Z","msg":"迎豐交通方便D,就算而家未有地鐵,坐巴士周圍去已經好方便,遲D地鐵通埋車會更好.<br />\n加上本身係名校網,將來要放應該都有D家長客,應該唔難放"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T07:14:22.000Z","msg":"個一房單位其實真係好細, 有細路真係唔知點住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08d5cc2cf669a6a336763e4a1960a39e78a6ed0f","tid":2203032,"uid":254158,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T12:32:35.000Z","msg":"一房真係for單身或者情侶only, 將價就貨我覺得地理位置上, 點都揀迎豐"},{"pid":"835e884e9c1c13cb95d9da868652e02ebcf8ea23","tid":2203032,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:13:24.000Z","msg":"夜晚行一轉, 你自己應該會有答案"},{"pid":"a0c982600d031f0e645f5fc9261a675c1f1abf17","tid":2203032,"uid":80507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:46:44.000Z","msg":"迎豐始終係土瓜灣上路交通好 去港島搭巴士好快<br />\n同埋冇ssp咁雜<br />\n你幾多個人住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1個都夠住既"},{"pid":"641cbb2bcc9692e9325c125a622962a328f4eb9a","tid":2203032,"uid":202367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:51:42.000Z","msg":"海柏匯個區係ssp 邊皮，已經無以前咁雜，未來應該會更好。加上踩住三條地鐵線，未計巴士都超方便。食野可以去ssp食小店或者去南昌新商場都得。"},{"pid":"70bccde56c3f53499defbea024fde63bac832981","tid":2203032,"uid":249242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T13:57:09.000Z","msg":"土瓜灣有屯馬線好有potential，我都睇緊。"},{"pid":"0193a4773352fa3e74076a131684f6cc04770d4d","tid":2203032,"uid":109453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"感謝甘多位既意見，已經決定迎豐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d4af267b320ae2b48aa9eae1553224486e11b9a","tid":2203